<plot>Salmagundi is a documentary film that asks the question, What does it mean to be an American? to the diverse group of people that inhabit the United States of America. The purpose of the film is to bring to light the vastness of the term American in part by interviewing an American-Indian Chief, a prominent Asian-American businessman, and a Mexican man going through the citizenship process.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?474768</url></doc>
